data.description: THIS HOME QUALIFIES FOR AN ASSUMABLE LOAN THRU THE VA WITH AN INTEREST RATE OF 2.625%, CALL FOR DETAILS!!!   Welcome to 925 Bethpage Drive, located in the highly sought-after Star Ranch community! With a spacious floor plan just over 3,400 square feet, this home encompasses everything you've been dreaming of, offering 5 bedrooms, 3.5 bathrooms, and a dedicated office, along with a generously sized upstairs game room offering so many possibilities.  From the moment you step inside, you'll be struck by the soaring 20 foot ceilings and abundance of natural light.  This open-concept floorplan is perfectly suited to the desires of today's homebuyers, providing an ideal space for gathering, entertaining, and creating memories with open pass throughs in the family room, kitchen and dining room spaces.  The oversized bedrooms in this home are truly impressive and feature walk-in closets.  For those seeking spacious bedrooms this home is must see!    Recent updates include fresh paint and new carpet and pad, installed as of September 2023.  The oversized cul-de-sac lot is truly one of the unique features of this home and sets it apart from so many others, mature shade trees and no neighbors behind offer backyard privacy.  Whether you enjoy sipping coffee on the front porch or having family and friends gather in the private backyard.  This home has it all.
